title: SOLID Principles for Writing Clean and Structured Code
description: Are you ready to learn how to write clean and structured code? In this video, we explore the SOLID principles in programming that will help you create high-quality, understandable, and maintainable code.

captions.text: Welcome to Managed Code! Let's explore the SOLID principles for writing clean software.
First up is the Single Responsibility Principle which keeps each component focused on one task.
